name: meowstic-male

flavor_text_entries.x:
When in danger, it raises its ears and
releases enough psychic power to
grind a 10-ton truck into dust.
flavor_text_entries.y:
The eyeball patterns on the interior of its ears
emit psychic energy. It keeps the patterns tightly
covered because that power is too immense.
flavor_text_entries.omega-ruby:
When in danger, it raises its ears and
releases enough psychic power to
grind a 10-ton truck into dust.
flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:
The eyeball patterns on the interior of its ears
emit psychic energy. It keeps the patterns tightly
covered because that power is too immense.
flavor_text_entries.sword:
Revealing the eyelike patterns on the insides of
its ears will unleash its psychic powers. It normally
keeps the patterns hidden, however.
flavor_text_entries.shield:
The defensive instinct of the males is strong.
It’s when they’re protecting themselves or their
partners that they unleash their full power.

form_descriptions: Male and female Meowstic have different level-up moves and hidden abilities.  While gender differences are not usually considered to be separate forms, Meowstic's are treated as such for practical purposes.
